content: A total of 3 hours of hiking! The hiking trail is well done. Parking is at Gyeonggi University public parking lot!
Beautiful Gwanggyosan ㅎ I think it would be better if there was no fine dust! I'll go climbing again in the fall ㅎ Mountain is healing itself~~~!
It runs until 5:30 pm. It is next to the 3rd Tunnel ticket office. It is good to be able to easily explore the non-armed area. The price is also cheap and good.
